headline: Invitation Homes Announces Acquisitions Update and Launch of Developer Lending Program
summary: DALLAS, June 02, 2025--Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE: INVH) ("Invitation Homes" or the "Company") today provided an acquisitions update and announced that it has entered into its first agreement to launch a developer lending program.
